text: Rountzenheim-Auenheim is a commune in the Bas-Rhin department in Grand Est in north-eastern France. It was established on 1 January 2019 by merger of the former communes of Rountzenheim (the seat) and Auenheim.Arrêté préfectoral 4 September 2018 ==See also== * Communes of the Bas-Rhin department ==References== * INSEE commune file Category:Communes of Bas-Rhin Category:States and territories established in 2019
